item.title: Harley-Davidson Muscles Up With Two Powerful New Bikes
item.description:
Harley-Davidson Muscles Up With Two Powerful New Bikes

Harley-Davidson hopes to rev up riders with the "sinister" black styling and raw power of their two latest performance bikes, the CVO Pro Street Breakout and Low Rider S. Both Harleys boast the Milwaukee company's most powerful engine, the Screamin' Eagle Twin Cam 110.
